HEADWORD: Longipennes
<hw>Lon`gi*pen"nes</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n. pl.</pos> <ety>[NL.,
from L. <ets>longus</ets> long + <ets>penna</ets> wing.]</ety>
<fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>A group of longwinged sea birds, including the
gulls, petrels, etc.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

